description:
Beginning a bold new direction in the second exciting year of BOOM! Studios' Farscape comics! Crichton's worst adversary, fandom's favorite villain, and one of science fiction's greatest antagonists finds himself deposed from his throne on Hyneria and making a bold new discovery that could put him back on top of the Uncharted Territories! Collecting the first four issues of the hit new series! Written by the Farscape creator Rockne S. O'Bannon and scripted by best-selling Star Trek novelist David Alan Mack!

Trade paperback collection of Farscape: Scorpius issues 0-3.
name: Let Sleeping Dogs Lie
